  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Scale up of ongoing Lebanese Red Cross multipurpose cash assistance program that targets both host community as well as Syrian Refugees&#xC2;&#xA0;
&#xC2;&#xA0;
Our initial concept note listed following examples of activities:

Conduct verifications and household assessments &#xE2;&#x20AC;&#x201C; To properly identify eligibility and non-duplication with other initiatives
Distribution of cash cards
Monthly loading of cash cards &#xE2;&#x20AC;&#x201C; Agreements with financial service providers secure preferable currency and exchange rates to protect against significant value shifts due to economic conditions


Conduct ongoing verification of households - to ensure cash support is reaching the right beneficiaries and all household information is kept up to date</narrative>
  </description>
